Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.27,0:00:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是～阳光明媚的周日早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.91,0:00:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噜呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要放回自然了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它原本就该生活在森林里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚还特意为我抓来  真是抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有的事  我也只是一心想让你们见一面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？这个…喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～住手住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以带他一起走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想和涅吉弟弟待在一起呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎喜欢涅吉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「啊」？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉做过一回卓柏卡布拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是感受到了同伴的气息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.84,0:01:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  不可以带走涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己独自回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以时常来玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有缘再见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在附近…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就在附近  父亲就在附近！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「不会感到寂寞！因为、我深信还会再见面的！」by 涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…这是我个人的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,×～不行～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然已经得知此事  我们又怎能「哦、是么」这样袖手旁观呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说得没错  涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是搭档啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一起寻找涅吉老师的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找寻找…  一起寻找…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,休息日集合还以为是什么大事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉  明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,信任搭档也非常重要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倘若拒绝后果或许不堪设想哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥  不如就这样诚心诚意地接受大家的帮助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:03:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莫…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…我明白了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,契约发动！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～真的变身了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉有些害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀哈  中国四千年都吓了一大跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看看…失败卡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,木乃香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和香小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功卡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啦啦队和…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的全员都是Cosplay Card呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有3张失败卡  成绩还不错啊  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是碰巧啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不管怎样还真壮观呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来即便是临时契约  31人也太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么连我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系呢  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「出门在外靠朋友」嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用比喻得如此牵强！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  便劳烦大家协助了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  先从哪儿开始调查呢  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咪啪～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱抱真开心呀  呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～真想就这样抱回家～！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！…不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在胡思乱想些什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然试图将大小姐给抱回家！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,万分抱歉  大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请忘记我刚才的发言！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系啦  快来抱抱～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…不！  不可以抱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是如此地不成熟…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…难保不会涌现出邪恶思想！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱抱～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅  请务必原谅！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,惟独此事请务必饶恕我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:17.17,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,抱抱～小刹～抱抱～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一如既往的相声…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相声么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…现在开始分头行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和古菲同学调查楼下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,楼上就拜托莳绘同学你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  古菲同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才起就在喝些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑醋  对健康有帮助…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你似乎醉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…不过算了  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  我们也出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:10.02,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,「哼、玩不下去了」by 伊文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,by 伊文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不协助搜寻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是Thousand Master哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即便遇见了他  也不可能会解除我身上的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反而只会令我感到不快…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,口是心非…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那装扮…很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…我宰了你哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:42.32,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,「好～了、要加油咯～」by 明日菜(失败卡形态)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,by 明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…  快看  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蔷薇？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蔷薇～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别玩了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蔷薇！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不理会我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这气息是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Thousand Master？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～发现证据！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  为什么会在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是某种提示吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,提示？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等着别人来发现自己吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打算做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ras tel ma scir magister
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连接光辉交换誓约的人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,万物的精灵啊  请指引我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,此时此地所追寻牵绊之主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉连这种魔法都会用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…拜托隆道教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是能够透视未来的放大镜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,史伽了不起～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  使用这个放大镜就能看见我们成为大人时的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀  这可真是有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就请先替在下看看未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是个出水芙蓉般的好女人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？  怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在下的未来究竟如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么不要啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难以启齿～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难以启齿！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  风香同学  史伽同学  能听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能够借助一下你们的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是证据啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就依靠两位小姑娘的魔幻推理啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Magical Roger！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…哪里魔幻了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:09:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这边…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或者这边么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非涅吉你选错人了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  先不管这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生过什么事了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  别有原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可告人的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在下的…未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  这样偷懒真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,休息片刻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用和香来试验？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,随身物品必须事先确认
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我会很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来  下一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是魔鬼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底也只是果汁  不会有生命危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么你自己不喝？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说有些对不住涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:11:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但在进行搜寻之前  必须先把这身装扮给拍摄下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法少女千羽  真燃(萌)！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,网络偶像No.1手到擒来！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法少女(cos)开始了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  这就魔法变身～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…这真的是魔法少女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,认输…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不必道歉  原本就是我的不情之请
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师真温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ras tel ma scir magister
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,木乃香！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小刹  再快些～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是！  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再快些～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是！  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:11:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎乐在其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似忘记了原本目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在下的未来究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将性命都悬于啦啦队的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…吾等3人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甘当老师的鹰犬也实属事出有因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然  哼哼  未曾有你这般恶贯满盈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,织线针之美砂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,溜溜球之圆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弹珠之樱子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吾等啦啦队参上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  赶快放了那位杂技少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恰恰相反！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…真能干！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔～～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,琉球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坂本九
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玩什么玩！  赶快帮忙找！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噢～！  真猛烈！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,轰轰轰轰轰轰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼～手指夹进小夹缝里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  笨手笨脚呐  裕奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  亚子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  似乎也不在这儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟在哪里呢  涅吉爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么呢  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…其实呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇！  真大！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塑料模型！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个包包里面似乎塞有我所想要的物品的半成品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…原来还未完成呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就这样想…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不如制造一个能够为我们搜索涅吉老师父亲所在地的人工卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  就是这玩意儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好！  将污损处加以干涂体现其真实感！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像德意志军一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…只是人工卫星诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:24.46,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,天文部&占卜研究会\N「开始联合研究吧～」会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那边  那边  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这可真方便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏美～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  还在搜索途中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,复原～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  千鹤姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这该怎么使用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是盘子呢…魔法盘…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了！  用这个端茶的话就会邂逅良缘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！  比如夹在腋下会长高…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快长高～快长高～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,长得高才怪～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:04.23,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,拉面  隆道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…辣椒酱么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧为墨西哥肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻辣得真是美味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…话说回来高畑老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,俄罗斯的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噢～俄式面包的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真不错  还有别的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高畑老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该继续搜寻了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？  灵光闪现！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想到了拉面新作…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,命名「肉包面」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是肉包？还是面？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不过也很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  那么我们就此告辞…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好！  立刻开始试作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  铃音  你们都来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight～！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  那边也一无所获啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说美空…那Cosplay真夸张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  在宿舍里分头寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真想试试变身后的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜不太懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  现在只好自食其力…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也超越本分地给予协助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来小莳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要叫莫兹父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这我也在意了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倘若你不介意的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  说起来还真没和大家提起过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看  这就是我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上个月刚拍的最新版
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？  仍旧健在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然了  别说那么不吉利的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  稍微有些失望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还敢说失望！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小莳的父亲真帅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？  是吗  嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…不太像啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真的耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哟  眼部附近难道不是很像么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这给人爽朗感觉之类的  没什么恶意～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爽朗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！  这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真像！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小莳  这条狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是「父亲」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非狗的名字也叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…「父亲」？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那条狗呢…自从来到我家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.46,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,(儿童节)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,充满活力的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:18:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依照惯例  亚星Mako
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我和父亲打招呼  它一定也会回过头来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是只伤脑筋的笨狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以无可奈何  就取名为「父亲」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？  怎么了…「父亲」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看  很像是吧  看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨狗  笨狗  笨狗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨狗～～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…「父亲」？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也难怪它想飞走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愿它在天国得以安息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,振作些  古菲同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了  这Cosplay重在「醉」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愈醉愈强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喝黑醋都会醉…呃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班长同学  能听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  涅吉老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是连我自己都感到欣慰的作品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好！  发射吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…如何将它搬出屋外？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我拥有探察香味的能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  使用这个能力的话  或许能够根据黑蔷薇找到父亲的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了  包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看见了  是湖畔！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来还是很在意嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是散步而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.21,0:20:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫兹  西奇米…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主人刚刚离去喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来还是决定了和你不告而别
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是Thousand Master的仆人喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就在刚才  这些都成为了历史
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们奉命成为今后涅吉弟弟的仆人了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有给你的留言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「茁壮成长吧！」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,茁壮成长吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.59,0:21:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,复原了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  这回持续时间可真长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉的力量啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:21:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:21:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不断在成长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:21:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照小鬼自己的方式…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.37,0:22:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲  我会努力的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不懈努力  成为像父亲一样的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.14,0:22:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请你好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.85,0:22:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.76,0:24:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.45,0:24:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.79,0:24:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.27,0:24:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快走吧  大家都等着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.18,0:24:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  不如来赛跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.05,0:24:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我可不会输哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.74,0:24:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.55,0:24:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.57,0:24:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.22,0:24:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法使的修行才刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.00,0:24:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和31位优秀的搭档共同努力！  涅吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.71,0:24:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以Magister Magi——你的父亲为目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.74,0:24:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,tel ma amorista！
